            <p style="margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-family: 'Microsoft Yahei', 微软雅黑, Tahoma, Arial, Helvetica, STHeiti;font-size: 12px;line-height: 18px;white-space: normal;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255)"><span style="font-family: 'Microsoft YaHei'; font-weight: bold; font-size: 18px;">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-family: 'Microsoft Yahei', 微软雅黑, Tahoma, Arial, Helvetica, STHeiti;font-size: 12px;line-height: 18px;white-space: normal;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255)"><span style="font-family: 'Microsoft YaHei'; font-weight: bold; font-size: 18px;">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; </span><span style="font-size: 16px;"><span style="font-family: 'Microsoft YaHei'; font-weight: bold;">&nbsp;<span style="font-family: 黑体, SimHei; font-weight: bold;">找煤网</span></span><span style="font-family: 'Microsoft YaHei';">（</span><span style="color: rgb(51, 127, 229); font-family: 'Microsoft YaHei';">www.zhaomei.com</span><span style="font-family: 'Microsoft YaHei';">）</span><span style="text-indent: 28px; font-family: 宋体;"><span style="font-family: 'Microsoft YaHei';">是由</span><span style="color: rgb(229, 51, 51); font-family: 'Microsoft YaHei';">浙江捷贸通电子商务有限公司</span><span style="font-family: 'Microsoft YaHei';">运营的第三方煤炭电子交易平台。平台于</span></span><span style="text-indent: 28px; font-family: 'Microsoft YaHei';">2015年6月10日正式上线。找煤网集煤炭供求资讯发布、撮合交易、金融、仓储、物流及第三方支付服务于一体，开设有特价专区和矿方直营专区，致力于为煤炭产业链用户提供一站式的电子交易解决方案。</span></span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-family: 'Microsoft Yahei', 微软雅黑, Tahoma, Arial, Helvetica, STHeiti;font-size: 12px;line-height: 18px;white-space: normal;background-color: white"><br></p><p style="margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-family: 'Microsoft Yahei', 微软雅黑, Tahoma, Arial, Helvetica, STHeiti;font-size: 12px;line-height: 18px;white-space: normal;background-color: white"><br></p><p style="margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-family: 'Microsoft Yahei', 微软雅黑, Tahoma, Arial, Helvetica, STHeiti;font-size: 12px;line-height: 18px;white-space: normal;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255)"><span style="font-size: 16px;"><span style="font-family: 黑体, SimHei; font-weight: bold;">我们的使命</span><span style="font-family: 'Microsoft YaHei'; font-weight: bold; line-height: 18px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">——</span></span><span style="font-size: 16px; font-family: 'Microsoft YaHei';">创新煤炭流通体系，促进产业优化升级</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-family: 'Microsoft Yahei', 微软雅黑, Tahoma, Arial, Helvetica, STHeiti;font-size: 12px;line-height: 18px;white-space: normal;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255)"><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-weight: bold; font-size: 16px;"><br></span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-family: 'Microsoft Yahei', 微软雅黑, Tahoma, Arial, Helvetica, STHeiti;font-size: 12px;line-height: 18px;white-space: normal;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255)"><span style="font-size: 16px;"><span style="font-family: 黑体, SimHei; font-weight: bold;"><span style="font-family: 黑体, SimHei; font-weight: bold; line-height: 18px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">我们的</span>愿景</span><span style="font-family: 'Microsoft YaHei'; font-weight: bold;">——</span></span><span style="font-size: 16px; font-family: 'Microsoft YaHei';">建设中国领先的煤炭全产业链电商平台</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-family: 'Microsoft Yahei', 微软雅黑, Tahoma, Arial, Helvetica, STHeiti;font-size: 12px;line-height: 18px;white-space: normal;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255)"><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-weight: bold; font-size: 16px;"><br></span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-family: 'Microsoft Yahei', 微软雅黑, Tahoma, Arial, Helvetica, STHeiti;font-size: 12px;line-height: 18px;white-space: normal;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255)"><span style="font-size: 16px;"><span style="font-family: 黑体, SimHei; font-weight: bold;"><span style="font-family: 黑体, SimHei; font-weight: bold; line-height: 18px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">我们的</span>口号</span><span style="font-family: 'Microsoft YaHei'; font-weight: bold;">——</span><span style="font-family: 'Microsoft YaHei';">找煤</span><span style="font-family: 'Microsoft YaHei';">够简单</span></span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-family: 'Microsoft Yahei', 微软雅黑, Tahoma, Arial, Helvetica, STHeiti;font-size: 12px;line-height: 18px;white-space: normal;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255)"><br></p><p style="margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-family: 'Microsoft Yahei', 微软雅黑, Tahoma, Arial, Helvetica, STHeiti;font-size: 12px;line-height: 18px;white-space: normal;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255)"><br></p><p style="margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-family: 'Microsoft Yahei', 微软雅黑, Tahoma, Arial, Helvetica, STHeiti;font-size: 12px;line-height: 18px;white-space: normal;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255)"><br></p><p style="margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-family: 'Microsoft Yahei', 微软雅黑, Tahoma, Arial, Helvetica, STHeiti;font-size: 12px;line-height: 18px;white-space: normal;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255)"><br></p><p style="margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;margin-left: 0;padding: 0px;font-family: 'Microsoft Yahei', 微软雅黑, Tahoma, Arial, Helvetica, STHeiti;font-size: 12px;line-height: 18px;text-indent: 0;white-space: normal;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255)"><span style="font-family: 黑体, SimHei; font-size: 16px;"><strong><span style="font-family: 黑体, SimHei;">煤炭交易配套服务</span></strong></span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;margin-left: 0;padding: 0px;font-family: 'Microsoft Yahei', 微软雅黑, Tahoma, Arial, Helvetica, STHeiti;font-size: 12px;line-height: 18px;text-indent: 0;white-space: normal;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255)"><br></p><p style="margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;margin-left: 0;padding: 0px;font-family: 'Microsoft Yahei', 微软雅黑, Tahoma, Arial, Helvetica, STHeiti;font-size: 12px;line-height: 18px;text-indent: 0;white-space: normal;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255)"><br></p><p style="margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;margin-left: 28px;padding: 0px;font-family: 'Microsoft Yahei', 微软雅黑, Tahoma, Arial, Helvetica, STHeiti;font-size: 12px;line-height: 18px;white-space: normal;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255)"><span style="font-size: 16px; font-family: 'Microsoft YaHei';">物流服务</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;margin-left: 28px;padding: 0px;font-family: 'Microsoft Yahei', 微软雅黑, Tahoma, Arial, Helvetica, STHeiti;font-size: 12px;line-height: 18px;white-space: normal;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255)"><span style="font-size: 16px; font-family: 'Microsoft YaHei';"><br></span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;margin-left: 0;padding: 0px;font-family: 'Microsoft Yahei', 微软雅黑, Tahoma, Arial, Helvetica, STHeiti;font-size: 12px;line-height: 18px;white-space: normal;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);text-indent: 28px"><span style="font-family: 'Microsoft YaHei'; font-size: 16px;">找煤网提供双向物流信息交流平台。用户可根据自己的需求选择运输方式，进行物流和运力的整合。从集货、存储、补货、混配、出货到配送，找煤网提供全程服务跟踪。为保证货物保质保量地送到客户手中，找煤网将提供全程第三方质检。</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;margin-left: 0;padding: 0px;font-family: 'Microsoft Yahei', 微软雅黑, Tahoma, Arial, Helvetica, STHeiti;font-size: 12px;line-height: 18px;white-space: normal;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);text-indent: 28px"><br></p><p style="margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;margin-left: 28px;padding: 0px;font-family: 'Microsoft Yahei', 微软雅黑, Tahoma, Arial, Helvetica, STHeiti;font-size: 12px;line-height: 18px;white-space: normal;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255)"><span style="font-family: Wingdings; font-weight: bold; font-size: 16px;"><br></span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;margin-left: 28px;padding: 0px;font-family: 'Microsoft Yahei', 微软雅黑, Tahoma, Arial, Helvetica, STHeiti;font-size: 12px;line-height: 18px;white-space: normal;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255)"><span style="font-size: 16px; font-family: 'Microsoft YaHei';">&nbsp;仓储服务</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;margin-left: 28px;padding: 0px;font-family: 'Microsoft Yahei', 微软雅黑, Tahoma, Arial, Helvetica, STHeiti;font-size: 12px;line-height: 18px;white-space: normal;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255)"><span style="font-size: 16px; font-family: 'Microsoft YaHei';"><br></span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;margin-left: 0;padding: 0px;font-family: 'Microsoft Yahei', 微软雅黑, Tahoma, Arial, Helvetica, STHeiti;font-size: 12px;line-height: 18px;white-space: normal;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);text-indent: 28px"><span style="font-family: 'Microsoft YaHei'; font-size: 16px;">&nbsp;对于沿海沿江港口的仓储堆存，找煤网可提供代收/发货的服务，费用更低更合理。同时，找煤网还提供港口社交、交流信息发布功能，便于最大程度整合周边客户资源。</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;margin-left: 0;padding: 0px;font-family: 'Microsoft Yahei', 微软雅黑, Tahoma, Arial, Helvetica, STHeiti;font-size: 12px;line-height: 18px;text-indent: 0;white-space: normal;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255)"><br></p><p style="margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;margin-left: 28px;padding: 0px;font-family: 'Microsoft Yahei', 微软雅黑, Tahoma, Arial, Helvetica, STHeiti;font-size: 12px;line-height: 18px;white-space: normal;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255)"><span style="font-family: Wingdings; font-weight: bold; font-size: 16px;"><br></span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;margin-left: 28px;padding: 0px;font-family: 'Microsoft Yahei', 微软雅黑, Tahoma, Arial, Helvetica, STHeiti;font-size: 12px;line-height: 18px;white-space: normal;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255)"><span style="font-size: 16px; font-family: 'Microsoft YaHei';">&nbsp;金融服务</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;margin-left: 28px;padding: 0px;font-family: 'Microsoft Yahei', 微软雅黑, Tahoma, Arial, Helvetica, STHeiti;font-size: 12px;line-heigh